proposal:
Hello DogeStarz community! 🐶🌟

Ever wondered what it would be like if DogeStarz had its own DEX or maybe a Lottery? Or even better, a DogeStarz IDO launchpad? Well, guess what? We can help you make that a reality! 

We offer a variety of B2B tools that can be customized to your project's needs. From creating your own DEX based on Uniswap V2 to setting up a blockchain-based lottery, we've got you covered. And the best part? All these tools are available at a revenue share price, meaning you don't have to pay anything upfront!

Here's a sneak peek of what we can offer:

1. 🔄 DEX (UNI FACTORY) - Imagine a DogeStarz DEX with your own colors, logo, and menus!
2. 🎰 Lottery - Because who doesn't love a good lottery, especially when it's on the blockchain?
3. 🪙 Wallet - A multicurrency crypto wallet with DogeStarz branding, anyone?
4. 🌾 Farming - Let's attract more investments by offering rewards.
5. 🗳 DAO - A platform for your stakeholders to create and vote for proposals.
6. 🌉 CrossChain - An EVM compatible blockchain bridge, because why not?
7. 🚀 IDOFactory - A DogeStarz Launchpad for IDO pools and token locking.

Remember, it's not about playing, it's about creating. So, let's create something amazing together! Check out our demo here: https://t.me/onoutdemos. Looking forward to hearing from you soon! 👋

P.S. We promise no dogs were harmed in the making of these tools! 🐶
